Class PartialConditionSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.analysis.GenericObject

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IdentHolder, ModelElement, ChannelDataHolder, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.undo.StateEditable
    public abstract class PartialConditionSet
extends ConditionSet
implements ModelElement
    This extension to ConditionSet allows the condition set to support a predefined list of components.

      • updateSelection

        public void updateSelection​(int[] newSelection)
        This method updates the components that are currently included in the condition set. This will remove entries from the condition set for the components that are removed from the selection, and dadd the entries to the condition set components added to the selection. The current value for condition sets will be stored.
        Parameters:
        newSelection - the int[] that contains the selected components.
